channel.title: Project CloudScape!
channel.description:
Hi, I'm going to be creating a new server and when you make a new server of course you'll need staff and coders!! If you apply for a job/possition you must be active, if your not active for a certain amount of time then your job will be taken by another person unless you tell me that you'll be away!
The new server will have: [code] 1. A custom spawn point 2. Harder training 3. Prices like regular RS 4. Gold will be harder to get 5. Mini Games ( Barrows/Castle Wars ) [/code]
If This server is used frequently, I will make a strand of them. The only way i'll ever post the server as a download is if my staff and coders agree to put it on the downloads page.
Jobs:
Coders: - Pureman0194 - Waffles!! - - - Moderators/Staff: - barkingdogc - Waffles!! - - - Testers: - dantotman - - Supporters: - - - - -
Jobs You Can Be: [code] 1. Coder 2. Mod/Staff 3. Server Tester 4. Supporter If you want to have Multi-Jobs put what you want to be on the bottom of the Application. [/code]
Application: [code] 1. Job: 2. Experience in that job: 3. How long have you known MoparScape: 4. How old are you: 5. How active will you be: 6. What's your Msn: [/code]
ONLY APPLY IF YOUR SERIOUS ABOUT CONTRIBUTING TO THIS SERVER! Other details about the server project will be told to you on Msn.
Thanks, Clouds Nobody
